,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c6e0d3d0cfdb25e5cb5dd303ce99978c146999c","tid":2006714,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"633d98d180c35a3351797fc679c322c807ae4c10","tid":2006714,"uid":217896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:23:15.000Z","msg":"Thx 會唔會好難預約"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:24:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DUTjyGA-Rno\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDUTjyGA-Rno&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0De9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=57c4a7c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DUTjyGA-Rno</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"就係呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係睇呢條片 就買左佢五一黃金周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:27:44.000Z","msg":"臨時臨急好難預約"},{"pid":"20064ddd8e5ca8747366e1b0faa111d9570389c6","tid":2006714,"uid":197028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T20:30:56.000Z","msg":"尋日去左之前見人係痴線西嗰邊介紹過既Adella beaute 順便係度包膠下<br />\n<br />\n之前有絲打介紹 已經follow左<br />\n跟住見佢有五一黃金週優惠 就約左黎試<br />\n<br />\n約既時候我係㩒美容師幫我揀<br />\n揀左美容師winnie(新美容師有-$10優惠)<br />\n最後佢推薦我做左aquapeel 係幾好 $254有full set facial做仲要唔伏.... 都做左幾多野下<br />\n如果按摩可以耐啲就更加好 佢肥肥地按得好舒服no offence<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有得單次比 仲要全程冇sell過<br />\n因為我唔太識拒絕 唔sell對我來講好重要!!<br />\n而且後尾睇返原來呢個係佢地最平既facial<br />\n原本我都驚驚地佢會逼我做啲貴野......<br />\n好有良心 痴線 仲要係黃店<br />\n佢地值得更多人認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題外話 雖然佢地有講岩岩搬舖<br />\n但舖頭門口招牌都冇個 我差啲入錯隔離美容院<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33989846c989f35a3cdb850e62f94eef70721eef","tid":2006714,"uid":249722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T20:34:23.000Z","msg":"搭單問 想清黑頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}